reviewText: This older movie was an excellent piece of work by Barbara Stanwyck.

Wonderful movie with Stany and Barry Sullivan. Good plot and lots of action. As usual these two actors are at their finest with the chemistry they shared. Beautiful scenery. Wonderful movie for the folks who like quality movies.
barbara stanwyck gave an excellent performance backed up by barry sullivan who doesnt seem to get the neccessary publicity he deserves. thank you

This movie contains many familiar things. One being the hotel where part of it takes place. I used to own that hotel in Silverton, CO. and the name of the hotel in real life is the Grand Imperial Hotel. Barbara Stanwyck is always good as the tough western lady.
